@startuml
title UC012 - Control Flow Diagram (Admin Approve/Reject Review)
start

:1. Admin selects "Review Request" to manage;
:2. Request review data;

:3. Fetch review data from database;
if (4. Is review data available?) then (yes)
  :5. Display review information to admin;
  :6. Admin selects approve or reject;

  if (7. Is review approved?) then (yes)
    :8. Update review status in database;
    :9. Display message ("Review approved");
    stop
  else (no)
    :10. Reject review and update database;
    :11. Display message ("Review rejected");
    stop
  endif
else (no)
  :12. Display message ("No review data found");
  - 1. Return to reviews page
  stop
endif

@enduml